Seahorse Spark docker image
===========================

The image contains Spark and python libraries required for running SX inside a docker container.

1. Building the image

   $ docker build -t quay.io/deepsense_io/deepsense-spark:2.0.0 .

2. Running the image

   $ docker run -h sandbox -d quay.io/deepsense_io/deepsense-spark:2.0.0
   $ docker run -it -p 8088:8088 -p 8042:8042 -p 4040:4040 -h sandbox quay.io/deepsense_io/deepsense-spark:2.0.0 bash

3. Publishing the image

   $ docker push quay.io/deepsense_io/deepsense-spark:2.0.0
